Blocks.Text: It 3'd Enown what it would be like Sid sooner
have married a parson. " He Rissed her. "Parsons
work on Sundays," he said. "they're worse off than
Submariners. You ought to have married that fat
starbroker chap and shared him with his three
mistresses. Anyway it might be much worse.
Pericles is a Portsmouth boat. She spends longer
in harbour than any other submarines.
